<div id="content"><a id="startcontent" name="startcontent"></a>  
<div id="content_title">Honors opportunities</div>

<blockquote>
<div id="content_text">

<p>At the Bren School, highly ambitious, talented undergraduate students succeed in preparing themselves for complex 
            and exciting careers. </p>
<p>Education extends from 
			    the classroom to the laboratory, studio, and library; undergraduate students have amazing opportunities to 
			    join faculty in research and have their work recognized 
			    in symposia and in print before graduating with a bachelor's degree. </p>
<p>All of this is available at the Bren School, along 
			    with honors programs and special honors-level advising 
			    to help students make the most of their education</p>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="4" width="100%">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td valign="top"><span style="color: #6699cc;"><strong>&#187;</strong></span></td>
<td valign="top"><strong>ICS H197: Honors Seminar</strong><br/>
                    Opportunity for undergraduate honors students to learn about the research taking place in the School and to begin to get involved with this research. <a href="honors_h197.php">more &#187;</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"><span style="color: #6699cc;"><strong>&#187;</strong></span></td>
<td valign="top"><strong>Bren School Honors Program</strong><br/>
                    Provides an opportunity for selected students in any of the School's majors to carry out a research project under the direction of a faculty member in the School. <a href="honors_program.php">more &#187;</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p>&#160;</p>


</div>
</blockquote>
